text: Terence D. Macaig (born October 23, 1938) is an American politician in the state of Vermont. He is a member of the Vermont House of Representatives, sitting as a Democrat from the Chittenden-2 district, having been first elected in 2008. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the Vermont House of Representatives Category:Vermont Democrats
title: Terence Macaig
